{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":10,"day":5}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"想念毛主席（藏族新民歌）","authors":[],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在起床的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想起了毛主席；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比阿爹还亲的亲人哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您给了牧民灿烂的黎明！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在放羊的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想起了毛主席；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比太阳还温暖的亲人哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您使草青水甜牛壮羊肥！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在打猎的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想起了毛主席；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您给我们钢枪和智慧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要扫尽一切恶兽和毒蛇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在喝奶茶的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想起了毛主席；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您赶跑了饥饿的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的碗里才不再装着眼泪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在唱山歌的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想起了毛主席；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您领导我们摧毁农奴制，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被封锁的歌喉才飞出歌声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，想念毛主席呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年万代不忘您的恩情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，想念毛主席呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千山万水永远闪耀您的光辉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（商文健整理）"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}